'''Dar es salaam school of Journalism''' is an institution based in the district of Ilala in [[Dar es Salaam]], [[Tanzania]] which offers courses in the fields of Journalism, Information Technology, Public Relations and Advertising. It was founded in 1998 and Registered by the National Council for Technical Education (NACTE).

